Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.94,Love Asteroid - Default,Mira,0,0,0,,Rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.17,Love Asteroid - Default,Tomori,0,0,0,,Chúng ta dùng luôn mấy ảnh chụp sao nhé?
